    <bodyBottom>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>If you need further support, don’t hesitate to reach out to <a href="mailto:studentservices@qmu.ac.uk" title="Student Services">Student Services </a>or your Personal Academic Tutor.</p>]]></Value>
