    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Supported by the Senior Leadership Team, staff across the University and Students’ Union have come together as a working group to ensure that we do everything we can to support students through the cost of living crisis. The work of the group is drawing on insight from students, and advice from relevant organisations. Through representative bodies, we are also working to make sure that government understands the issues affecting students.</p>
<p>On this page, you will find information on facilities and resources to help you with the cost of living crisis. We will keep this list updated.</p>
<p>If you would like to share your thoughts please email our <a href="mailto:studentservices@qmu.ac.uk" title="Email student services">working group.</a></p>]]></Value>
    </introduction>
